{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_06_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 ドラマの中のことなのに",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、ちょうど良かった\n今から、葵を探しに行こうとしてたところだったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ just in time.\nI was about to go look for Aoi.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.266666611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 6.6278459867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……何かあったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6278459867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "葵に仕事の話がきてな\n今までと毛色が違うから、まずは相談しないとと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's a job offer for you‚ Aoi.\nIt's a bit different from what you've done before‚ so I thought I'd discuss it with you first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.7000008345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 16.1967131854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "君は僕達のマネージャーなんだから\nいちいち僕に相談しないで、OKしても良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're our manager.\nYou could have just accepted it without consulting me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.7633798521,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 22.230046646
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一体{user}君が\n悩むほどの仕事ってなんなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what kind of job is it that\nhas {user} so concerned?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3967133126,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、前にすずがドラマにゲスト出演しただろう？\n毎週、殺人事件を解決していく……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Remember when Suzu guest-starred on that drama?\nThe one where they solve a murder case every week…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.5333332778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 34.4880729836
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あれ。僕も観たよ\n今度は僕に、あのドラマへの出演依頼がきたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that one. I watched it too.\nSo‚ now they're asking me to star on that drama?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2214063169,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 42.3547381243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それで、僕は一体何をすればいいんだい\n死体役？　スキップしながら包丁振り回すとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I supposed to do?\nPlay a corpse? Or running around waving a knife?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7547381243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……結構やる気だな\nダンス以外の仕事は嫌がるかと思ってたんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You seem pretty eager.\nI thought you'd dislike work outside of dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1999968927,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 55.9294088126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワの躍進のためにはなんでもやると言ったからね\n演技は未経験だけど、頑張ってみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said I'd do anything for LizNoir's success.\nI have no acting experience‚ but I'll give it my best shot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.0627421459,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 62.9960749706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それに殺陣は一度、ちゃんとやってみたかったんだ\nいい人に教えてもらえるなら、ありがたいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ I've always wanted to try action scenes properly.\nIf I can learn from someone good‚ that would be great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.629408304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 70.0627385855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや……葵にやってほしいのは\n周りから交際を反対されてるカップルの役だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… The role they want you to play\nis part of a couple whose relationship is opposed by those around them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.8666610162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "いわば、ロミオとジュリエットみたいな関係だな\nそれが事件後にやっと結ばれる……って筋書きらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's kind of like Romeo and Juliet.\nThey finally get together after the incident… that's the storyline.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2793136832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 84.6825869482
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ロミオとジュリエット……\nつまり、恋愛がメインってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Romeo and Juliet…\nSo‚ it's mainly a romance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6492536148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "ってことは、男の人と付き合う場面とか\nデートシーンなんかもあるのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Does that mean there'll be scenes of me going out with‚\nand dating a guy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9825910171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 98.7825910171
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "僕、デートなんてしたことも\n何をするのか考えたことも、ろくにないんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never been on a date.\nI haven't even really thought about what to do on one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7492576838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 105.3492561579
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ま……まぁ、撮影では台本もあるから\nデートの内容で悩むことはない……と、思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… there'll be a script for the shoot‚ so\nyou shouldn't have to worry about what to do on the date… I think.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6000040133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "それもそうか\nで、『やっと結ばれる』っていうのは、どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true.\nSo‚ what does \"finally get together\" mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9286439737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "rouka",
      "startTime": 119.3619773071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、資料の最後に書いてあったんだ\nウエディングドレスでの結婚式の撮影もあります、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ it was written at the end of the materials.\nThere's also going to be a wedding scene where you'll be in a wedding dress.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.66667068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office_yuugata",
      "startTime": 127.8951845249
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマの仕事の件、保留にしてもらって悪かったね\nリズノワのためならなんでもやると言ったばかりなのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for putting the drama job on hold.\nI did say I'd do anything for LizNoir…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2618537347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "あの後、莉央達にも相談してみたんだ\nあまりに無様だと、リズノワの評判にも関わるからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ I talked to Rio and the others about it.\nIt could affect LizNoir's reputation if it's too clumsy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5618527174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだけど、莉央はドラマのことを聞くなり\n目頭を押さえて泣き始めちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But when I mentioned the drama to Rio‚\nshe started crying‚ saying",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.1618659417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "「葵がお嫁に行ってしまうと想像したら、つい」\n……って。結婚式はドラマの中のことだっていうのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"Just imagining Aoi getting married made me cry.\"\n…Even though it's just part of the drama.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.3285315911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマに出るだけであの様子じゃ\n僕が本当に結婚する時は、どうなるんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just starring on the drama seems to have Rio worried…\nI wonder what it'll be like when I really get married.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.3951901197,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今はまだそんな予定はないからね\nあくまで莉央が心配ってだけだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ there are no plans for that yet.\nI'm just worrying about Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.4951982577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ葵が大事なんだろう……\nこころと愛は、なんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It just shows how much Rio cares about you…\nWhat about Kokoro and Ai?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.8666691541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "愛は「ウエディングドレス、似合いますよ！」って\nせっかくなんだしやればいいのにって言ってた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As for Ai‚ she said‚ \"You'd look great in a wedding dress!\"\nand urged me to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.1583348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi019.m4a",
      "text": "こころは……「葵さん、やりたくないんですか？」\n「その仕事、代わりにやりましょうか～？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And as for Kokoro… \"Aoi-san‚ don't you want to do it?\"\n\"Shall I do the job for youuu?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.0250015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi020.m4a",
      "text": "「でも葵さんより似合っちゃうかもしれませんね～」\n「って、愛ちゃんが言ってました！」……ってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"But it might suit me better than youuu\"\n\"…That's what Ai-chan said!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.3583348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こころのやつ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that Kokoro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.4916671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi021.m4a",
      "text": "こころはまだ子供だからね\nドレスを着て、お姫様気分にでもなってみたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is still a kid‚ after all.\nShe wants to put on a dress and feel like a princess.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.1908137004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "葵は、ウエディングドレスにはあまり興味ないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi‚ are you not interested in wearing a wedding dress?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 214.8908055623,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi022.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃ、どういうものかは知ってるけど\n着てみたいと思ったことは特にないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I know what it is‚\nbut I've never really wanted to wear one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.9502316554,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi023.m4a",
      "text": "自分でもしばらく考えてみたけど\nやっぱり、恋愛とか結婚のイメージなんてわかないし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I've thought about it‚\nI don't really have an image of love or marriage‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 228.5168962876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi024.m4a",
      "text": "いくら台本があるとは言っても\nさすがに何も思い浮かばないまま演技なんて出来ないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so even with a script‚\nI can't act without any ideas in mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.9835629542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi025.m4a",
      "text": "大体、表情の変化に乏しいとかよく言われるのに\nその僕に演技をしろだなんて。人選ミスじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They often say I lack expression‚\nso asking me to act is a mistake‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.5168962876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi026.m4a",
      "text": "そのくらい、{user}君が\n僕に話を振る前に気付いて、断ってほしかったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ you should have noticed that\nand declined before asking me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.7168973048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "いや……不慣れなことでも、やってみるからこそ\n新しい発見があるんじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… it's precisely because it's something new to do.\nWho knows‚ maybe there's something to learn from it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.7333337862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "「リズノワのためならなんでもやる」と言ったのも\n成長のためには、それが必要だと思ったからだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said you'd do anything for LizNoir\nbecause you thought it was necessary for growth‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.0124212461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi027.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。同じことばかりやっていたって\nそのうち頭打ちになるだけだし……けどねえ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ doing the same thing\nall the time will only lead to hitting the wall… But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.0171697855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "それに、葵に表現力がないなんてことはない\nダンスだって、表現であることに変わりない訳だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ Aoi‚ you're not lacking in expression.\nDance is still a form of expression.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.4333480278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi028.m4a",
      "text": "そりゃあ、そうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ that's true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.1881792863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "葵ならきっと、ダンス以外の表現も出来るはずだ\n演技を勉強するのも今後の役に立つと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure you can express yourself in ways other than dancing.\nLearning acting might be useful for your future roles.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.2666996716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_06_01-aoi029.m4a",
      "text": "……分かったよ\nそのドラマの仕事、やってみる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okay.\nI'll try doing that drama job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 297.13928411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
